# Frontend env (Vite)

Copy to `.env.local` for local overrides (gitignored by Vite).

```bash
# Dev defaults (see src/api.ts) already hit http://127.0.0.1:8000
# Only set these when pointing at a remote API:

# VITE_API_BASE=https://your-api-host.example.com
# VITE_WS_URL=wss://your-api-host.example.com/ws/live
# Optional; otherwise derived from VITE_WS_URL by replacing /ws/live with /ws/drone.
# VITE_DRONE_WS_URL=wss://your-api-host.example.com/ws/drone
# VITE_CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=

# Optional future Supabase client (map uses FastAPI today):
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
```

On **Vercel**, set the same `VITE_*` keys in Project → Settings → Environment Variables, then redeploy.
